verbose_text: While low Rab1B expression is reportedly correlated with poor prognosis of BC, downregulation of Rab1B was found to promote triple negative breast cancer (TNBC) metastasis by activating transforming growth factor-beta / mothers against decapentaplegic homolog signaling.
evidence: Rab1B was found to promote triple-negative breast cancer (TNBC) metastasis
